{
  "stem": "12868.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And later, they took a hospital where older people was and they-- and they burn up the doctors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the ghetto, they burn up the doctors with the nurses with all the-- all-- all the elderly people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they bun them up them alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They told the doctors not to leave, not to leave the hospital, and the nurses not to leave the hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If somebody-- they're going to leave, he'd-- he'd be shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put the gasoline.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they burned up the whole hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody see this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody see how they burn up this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What you can do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are like-- you are like animals between barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you can do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On this I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody, a lot  of us was lucky would go into the  work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they go into work, you took something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had sometimes, you had a little vase, or you had an extra shirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with the Gentile people, you trade them for a loaf of bread, for a piece of butter, or a piece of meat, some kind.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you got to hide this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in the ghetto, when you come back to work, and they found out you've got something, you get killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you got-- I remember when I-- I brought sometimes for a shirt, I had a piece of meat, you know, raw meat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I dropped down the meat around my legs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they searched me, they didn't search-- the-- I took a chance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because everybody knows that tomorrow, or next day, you get killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody would be alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we took a chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this what keep up my family when my father couldn't go to the work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was already old.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
